/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7557073cdd19315ae133238eee270bdd3fe40987","tid":102883,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aafc9240d7707cba5bc1e6a4eb12f53821723276","tid":102883,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要派畀冇交稅個班 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到班 中學雞 大學雞 拎哂去 買 iphone 去旅行<br />\n<br />\n將納稅人既錢送畀外國人   真係講粗口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算唔派，香港人都愈黎愈唔係香港洗錢嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n同一件貨香港貴過外國幾倍<br />\n同一種享受外國只係平民價錢<br />\n而家連窮人都買幾百蚊平飛去日台韓買日用品<br />\n仲方便過去澳門<br />\n<br />\n怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家係香港最大支出係食, 因食真係無得去外國先食.<br />\n我得番渣車但講真近年都無咩心機渣, 到到停車場都爆到痴線.<br />\n其他真係接近零消費, 要買野就托去旅行既FD或者自己去旅行買."},{"pid":"8f35d1f0ef89aeafb8ee075e8dc3c5829c7a2279","tid":102883,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用黎成立港人港地基金, 只起夾心階層樓俾有香港身份證首置既人買.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪以為班蝗全部都冇香港身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc8b0af7b12555fb04d445de1705be73a126eb8","tid":102883,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:52:23.000Z","msg":"有錢派就少d人反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebd7060b4521804643fcdc3c6940747eb8b5496","tid":102883,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"我認同政府無所為嘅情況下，應該套現比返納稅人好過，但強調係退稅，而唔係直接派錢"},{"pid":"50f6c5562fa18b91d354a438a499c6680ee1f2c4","tid":102883,"uid":55466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:57:06.0